00:36:59.217 --> 00:37:00.759
Dobro došao u borbu.

00:37:10.395 --> 00:37:12.688
<i>Evo kako ubiješ vrstu.</i>

00:37:13.440 --> 00:37:17.776
<i>Prvo pobiješ lake mete:
slabe, izložene.</i>

00:37:20.113 --> 00:37:22.781
<i>Ubiješ ih što učinkovitije.</i>

00:37:24.242 --> 00:37:26.368
<i>To su bila prva tri vala.</i>

00:37:27.704 --> 00:37:31.498
<i>No i ako bombama središ
kuću, ostane nekoliko žohara.</i>

00:37:32.542 --> 00:37:34.835
<i>Mi smo poput tih žohara.</i>

00:37:35.337 --> 00:37:37.671
<i>A Drugi nas ubijaju.</i>

00:37:38.632 --> 00:37:40.424
